ActFarm Credit Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of JANE HALFORD of Edmonton, Alberta, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Farm Credit Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective December 15, 2014, in the place of John Klippenstein.
